Texts.Eng: ... Floran has no one to play console with now...
Texts.Chs: ... 叶族人现在没有人可以玩游戏机了。。。

Texts.Eng: A beautifully made television stand, if there ever was one.
Texts.Chs: 一个制作精美的电视台，如果有的话。

Texts.Eng: A standard issue Protectorate dorm room television stand. This one comes with a console!
Texts.Chs: 一个标准的大地守护团宿舍电视台。这台有控制台！

Texts.Eng: Hah! I hardly ever had this television to myself back at the Academy...
Texts.Chs: 哈！我在学院里几乎没有一台电视。。。

Texts.Eng: I suppose I finally have the TV to myself now...
Texts.Chs: 我想我现在终于有了自己的电视。。。

Texts.Eng: In retrospect, the furniture of the Protectorate was remarkably and stylishly made.
Texts.Chs: 回首往事，大地守护团的家具制作得非常引人注目，非常时髦。

Texts.Eng: Oh man... It's even loaded up with the same games we had... This is just...
Texts.Chs: 天哪。。。甚至还有我们玩过的游戏。。。这只是。。。

Texts.Eng: This television was awfully great for hangin' out around.
